statements: SELECT * FROM Outreach_Programs;
SELECT program_name, target_community FROM Outreach_Programs WHERE outreach_status = TRUE;
SELECT * FROM Outreach_Programs WHERE outreach_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT program_name, outreach_date FROM Outreach_Programs ORDER BY outreach_date DESC;
SELECT program_name, target_community FROM Outreach_Programs WHERE target_community = 'School' AND outreach_status = TRUE;
SELECT program_name, target_community, outreach_date FROM Outreach_Programs WHERE outreach_status = TRUE ORDER BY outreach_date DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM Outreach_Programs WHERE outreach_status = FALSE ORDER BY program_id ASC LIMIT 3;
SELECT program_name AS Name, target_community AS Community, outreach_date AS Date FROM Outreach_Programs WHERE outreach_date >= '2022-01-01' AND outreach_status = TRUE ORDER BY outreach_date ASC;
SELECT program_name, target_community FROM Outreach_Programs WHERE target_community = 'Urban' OR target_community = 'Rural' ORDER BY program_name ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT program_name, outreach_date FROM Outreach_Programs WHERE target_community = 'Suburban' ORDER BY outreach_date DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT * FROM Outreach_Programs;
SELECT program_name, outreach_date FROM Outreach_Programs ORDER BY outreach_date DESC;
SELECT program_id, program_name, outreach_date FROM Outreach_Programs WHERE effectiveness_rating > 3 ORDER BY program_name;
SELECT program_id, program_name, outreach_date, effectiveness_rating FROM Outreach_Programs WHERE effectiveness_rating < 3 AND outreach_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM Community_Health_Status ORDER BY community_name ASC, outreach_date DESC;
SELECT program_name, outreach_date, effectiveness_rating FROM Outreach_Programs WHERE community_id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000';
SELECT program_id, program_name, outreach_date FROM Outreach_Programs WHERE effectiveness_rating > 3 ORDER BY outreach_date DESC;

SELECT program_name, outreach_date, community_name FROM Outreach_Programs JOIN Community_Health_Status ON Outreach_Programs.program_id = Community_Health_Status.outreach_program_id WHERE Community_Health_Status.health_status = 'Good';
SELECT * FROM Outreach_Programs WHERE program_name LIKE 'C%' OR program_name LIKE 'H%';
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_programs FROM Outreach_Programs;
SELECT * FROM OutreachPrograms;
SELECT program_name, community_target FROM OutreachPrograms WHERE start_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT participant_name, community, enrollment_date FROM ProgramParticipants WHERE completion_date IS NULL;
SELECT program_name, end_date FROM OutreachPrograms ORDER BY end_date DESC;
SELECT program_id, outreach_score, data_update_date FROM ProgramEfficacy WHERE outreach_score > 80;
SELECT program_name, community_target, start_date, end_date FROM OutreachPrograms;
SELECT * FROM ProgramParticipants WHERE completion_date IS NOT NULL;
SELECT participant_name, program_name, enrollment_date FROM ProgramParticipants JOIN OutreachPrograms ON ProgramParticipants.program_id = OutreachPrograms.program_id;
SELECT program_id, outreach_score, outreach_effectiveness FROM ProgramEfficacy WHERE outreach_score > 80 ORDER BY data_update_date DESC;

SELECT program_name, community_target, COUNT(program_id) AS participants_count FROM OutreachPrograms JOIN ProgramParticipants ON OutreachPrograms.program_id = ProgramParticipants.program_id GROUP BY program_id HAVING participants_count > 10;
SELECT * FROM outreach_programs;
SELECT program_name, outreach_location FROM outreach_programs WHERE start_date < '2022-01-01';
SELECT participants.participant_name, programs.program_name FROM program_participants participants JOIN outreach_programs programs ON participants.program_id = programs.program_id;
SELECT feedback_text, rating FROM participant_feedback WHERE rating > 3 ORDER BY feedback_date DESC;
SELECT program_name, num_participants, success_metric FROM program_performance ORDER BY num_participants DESC;
SELECT * FROM outreach_programs;
SELECT program_name, start_date, end_date FROM outreach_programs WHERE start_date >= '2022-01-01' AND end_date <= '2022-12-31';
SELECT outreach_location, target_community FROM outreach_programs ORDER BY outreach_location DESC;
SELECT participant_name, age, gender FROM program_participants WHERE age >= 18 AND gender = 'Male';
SELECT feedback_id, feedback_date, rating FROM participant_feedback WHERE rating > 3 ORDER BY feedback_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM Outreach_Programs;
SELECT program_name, program_description FROM Outreach_Programs WHERE program_date = '2022-01-01';
SELECT program_name, target_community FROM Outreach_Programs WHERE program_id IN (1, 3, 5);
SELECT participant_name, participant_age, participant_gender FROM Participants WHERE program_id = 2 ORDER BY participant_age DESC;

SELECT participant_name, engagement_date, engagement_type, engagement_notes FROM Participants p JOIN Engagement_Records e ON p.participant_id = e.participant_id WHERE p.participant_age > 20 ORDER BY engagement_date ASC;
SELECT * FROM Outreach_Programs ORDER BY program_name DESC;
SELECT program_name, program_date FROM Outreach_Programs WHERE program_date >= '2022-01-01';

SELECT p.participant_name, e.engagement_date, h.outcome_metrics FROM Participants p JOIN Engagement_Records e ON p.participant_id = e.participant_id JOIN Health_Outcomes h ON p.participant_id = h.participant_id WHERE e.engagement_type = 'Follow-up';
SELECT COUNT(*) AS total_participants, AVG(participant_age) AS avg_age FROM Participants WHERE participant_gender = 'Female';

SELECT c.community_name, c.community_population, COUNT(p.participant_id) AS total_participants FROM Community_Details c LEFT JOIN Participants p ON c.community_id = p.program_id GROUP BY c.community_name ORDER BY total_participants DESC;
